WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.940
=Episode 10=

01:42.050 --> 01:42.890
Uncle Lei,

01:43.020 --> 01:45.020
you must know about Yin Dai
stealing the credit.

01:45.620 --> 01:46.930
Why did you never tell me?

01:46.930 --> 01:48.096
What good would it have done?

01:48.850 --> 01:50.180
So many people saw it.

01:50.570 --> 01:52.130
Who ever spoke a word of justice?

01:52.210 --> 01:53.660
But with my mother's temperament,

01:54.820 --> 01:56.020
how could she endure it?

01:56.900 --> 01:58.490
Your mother was furious at first.

01:58.980 --> 01:59.980
But think about it.

02:00.290 --> 02:01.850
Your aunt was gravely injured

02:02.100 --> 02:03.460
and didn't want to be disturbed.

02:03.850 --> 02:04.690
Moreover...

02:05.740 --> 02:06.846
My mother had anticipated

02:06.857 --> 02:08.490
that the demonic sect
would seek revenge?

02:08.700 --> 02:10.300
Though Nie Hengcheng was killed,

02:10.980 --> 02:13.420
his disciples were vicious and powerful.

02:14.220 --> 02:15.980
Yin Dai took the credit,

02:16.340 --> 02:18.300
so he naturally had to bear
their retaliation.

02:21.260 --> 02:22.100
So,

02:22.620 --> 02:23.460
was Siqi Sect

02:23.820 --> 02:25.180
massacred by the demonic sect

02:25.950 --> 02:27.180
because of this?

02:27.540 --> 02:28.380
Yes.

02:28.860 --> 02:30.140
Yang Yi died an untimely death

02:30.260 --> 02:31.180
in that massacre.

02:31.540 --> 02:33.300
Only Yang Heying was left.

02:33.660 --> 02:35.060
The Yang clan then declined.

02:36.020 --> 02:37.053
All matters in this world

02:37.100 --> 02:38.780
are but reaping what one has sown.

02:40.460 --> 02:41.860
Cause and effect cycle endlessly;

02:41.940 --> 02:43.380
retribution never fails.

02:43.740 --> 02:44.580
Master.

02:46.460 --> 02:47.300
Zhao.

02:50.460 --> 02:51.300
Xiuming.

02:54.660 --> 02:56.426
The medicine for you
has just been prepared.

02:56.620 --> 02:57.330
Zhao,

02:57.376 --> 02:58.356
take it to your master.

02:58.460 --> 02:59.300
Alright.

03:01.300 --> 03:02.140
Thank you, Xiuming.

03:07.220 --> 03:08.060
Master.

03:11.820 --> 03:12.660
Yunke,

03:12.900 --> 03:14.060
where do you plan

03:14.220 --> 03:15.140
to bury Qiu?

03:17.340 --> 03:19.100
After all, we were fellow disciples.

03:19.500 --> 03:20.340
I think

03:20.940 --> 03:21.780
we should put him

03:22.220 --> 03:23.940
in the ancestral hall of Qingque Sect.

03:24.540 --> 03:25.840
The Yin family's ancestral hall?

03:28.260 --> 03:29.100
Master,

03:30.180 --> 03:32.460
Uncle Qiu would rather die
than turn back.

03:32.940 --> 03:33.780
Perhaps

03:34.820 --> 03:36.653
he wouldn't wish
to enter the ancestral hall.

03:38.860 --> 03:40.060
Zhao is making a point.

03:41.060 --> 03:41.900
Then I'll find

03:42.940 --> 03:44.060
another place for him.

03:45.300 --> 03:46.140
By the way, Zhao,

03:47.020 --> 03:47.860
that day,

03:48.020 --> 03:49.340
when you fought that villain,

03:49.420 --> 03:50.660
did you see his appearance?

03:51.980 --> 03:52.860
From head to toe,

03:53.460 --> 03:54.400
he was tightly covered.

04:01.380 --> 04:02.620
But I felt

04:03.526 --> 04:04.752
his bearing was extraordinary.

04:05.620 --> 04:06.940
Extraordinary bearing?

04:10.620 --> 04:13.300
(Chuitian Dock)

04:13.300 --> 04:14.140
This saliva

04:14.260 --> 04:15.580
is so miraculous.

04:16.540 --> 04:18.140
I'll go fetch some more for you.

04:18.500 --> 04:19.340
No need.

04:19.500 --> 04:21.810
Uncle Lei said the saliva
can warm the meridians,

04:22.020 --> 04:23.300
but it can only help me recovery

04:23.500 --> 04:24.340
to this point.

04:26.700 --> 04:27.540
Zhao.

04:28.460 --> 04:29.740
Why did Qian Xueshen

04:30.380 --> 04:32.380
hand over the saliva once you left?

04:34.700 --> 04:35.720
He must be touched

04:36.040 --> 04:37.170
by my sincerity.

04:38.300 --> 04:39.140
And then

04:40.300 --> 04:41.580
he died from poison?

04:42.260 --> 04:43.210
The demonic sect

04:43.220 --> 04:44.820
had long planted poison in him.

04:45.180 --> 04:46.220
By the time I arrived,

04:46.231 --> 04:47.200
it was already too late.

04:48.860 --> 04:49.700
Alas.

04:51.100 --> 04:53.220
Qian Xueshen is gone.

04:54.460 --> 04:55.300
Then,

04:55.420 --> 04:56.380
what about Chang?

04:57.260 --> 04:58.380
Did you meet him?

04:58.620 --> 04:59.460
Did he help?

05:00.660 --> 05:01.500
No.

05:01.580 --> 05:02.420
I didn't see him.

05:03.100 --> 05:03.940
No one helped me.

05:04.300 --> 05:05.260
Who knows where he went?

05:07.660 --> 05:08.500
Zhao,

05:10.180 --> 05:11.940
you really didn't go
to the snow mountains?

05:12.260 --> 05:13.100
Of course, I didn't.

05:14.220 --> 05:16.260
Those snow mountains are far away.

05:17.140 --> 05:19.140
How could I travel back and forth
in half a month?

05:22.900 --> 05:24.100
Now that the crisis has passed,

05:24.340 --> 05:26.380
you should rest and recover.

05:27.300 --> 05:28.860
I asked my mother about the treasure

05:29.279 --> 05:30.340
that can cure Nether Aura.

05:30.620 --> 05:31.773
She couldn't remember clearly

05:31.980 --> 05:33.420
and said she needs to look again

05:33.540 --> 05:35.373
through the notes and letters
left by my aunt.

05:37.500 --> 05:38.340
My mother

05:38.700 --> 05:40.540
and my grandfather owe Luoying Valley.

05:41.060 --> 05:42.460
Yet you're still willing to help me.

05:43.460 --> 05:44.620
I'm deeply grateful.

05:47.380 --> 05:49.940
If you truly feel sorry,

05:50.420 --> 05:51.260
why not pick

05:51.660 --> 05:53.260
a few treasures from Guangtian Sect

05:54.860 --> 05:56.340
and give them to me?

05:59.220 --> 06:00.980
You can have anything

06:01.360 --> 06:02.580
that Guangtian Sect and I have.

06:04.220 --> 06:05.860
Thank you in advance.

06:08.260 --> 06:09.100
This money

06:09.300 --> 06:11.340
is enough for you to open several shops.

06:14.380 --> 06:15.293
Where did it come from?

06:16.100 --> 06:17.300
Zhao, you've struck it rich.

06:17.460 --> 06:18.700
Yuzhi's payment to me.

06:19.580 --> 06:20.740
The saliva is expensive.

06:21.246 --> 06:22.649
Does that mean Yuzhi's cultivation

06:22.660 --> 06:24.660
can recover with the saliva?

06:25.020 --> 06:26.140
He's not fully recovered,

06:26.700 --> 06:27.620
but he's been better.

06:28.200 --> 06:29.369
If he wants a complete cure,

06:29.380 --> 06:30.780
he'll still need a healing treasure.

06:32.220 --> 06:33.620
Heaven truly envies talent.

06:33.980 --> 06:36.340
Uncle said Chang's poison
has also not been fully cured

06:36.580 --> 06:38.130
and still needs an antidote.

06:42.060 --> 06:43.900
Take out the remaining saliva.

06:44.166 --> 06:45.853
- My wounds haven't healed.
- Take it out.

06:45.866 --> 06:47.333
- I can't win.
- Take out the saliva.

06:47.660 --> 06:49.300
You soaked in the Wanzai Hot Spring

06:49.340 --> 06:50.180
for quite some time.

06:50.260 --> 06:51.300
Your injuries have healed.

06:51.500 --> 06:53.380
Only one of his poisons
remains hard to remove.

06:53.540 --> 06:54.520
So, he still needs rest.

06:56.020 --> 06:56.860
Zhao,

06:57.300 --> 06:58.980
that day at the Dusk Palace,

06:59.060 --> 07:01.300
you accused Ning
of being a demonic sect spy.

07:01.300 --> 07:02.140
Was that true?

07:02.220 --> 07:03.180
Of course not.

07:03.620 --> 07:04.546
That was just for show.

07:04.860 --> 07:06.260
Otherwise, how could we

07:06.500 --> 07:07.596
draw them out

07:07.607 --> 07:08.847
and expose the Body Shift plot?

07:10.220 --> 07:11.420
That's what I thought.

07:11.780 --> 07:13.420
Chang's acting was so convincing.

07:14.300 --> 07:16.700
That reaction had me thinking
he truly fled in fear of guilt.

07:17.940 --> 07:20.060
Then where is Ning now?

07:21.300 --> 07:22.260
Who knows?

07:22.553 --> 07:24.380
Maybe he's hiding somewhere
enjoying himself.

07:24.380 --> 07:25.380
Now that he's healed,

07:26.533 --> 07:28.179
he's probably making
a fortune somewhere.

07:28.420 --> 07:29.860
Anyway, he never wanted to stay here.

07:31.340 --> 07:33.100
Didn't he swear
to avenge his father before?

07:33.260 --> 07:34.740
People change.

07:35.660 --> 07:37.860
He might've made another decision.

07:47.660 --> 07:50.620
(Li Sect, Youming Path)

08:15.718 --> 08:17.098
(Yu Huiyin, Strategist of Li Sect)

08:17.109 --> 08:17.822
Young...

08:18.500 --> 08:19.340
Mu Qingyan,

08:19.660 --> 08:20.740
you're still alive.

08:21.900 --> 08:23.540
A mere injury from the Wudu Palm.

08:24.060 --> 08:25.060
What's so hard to cure?

08:26.740 --> 08:28.140
Go back and tell Nie Zhe

08:28.700 --> 08:30.240
that the Young Master is back

08:30.460 --> 08:32.060
and will reclaim everything that belongs

08:32.340 --> 08:33.180
to the Mu clan.

08:52.060 --> 08:55.620
♪Green robes, oh green robes♪

08:55.660 --> 08:58.860
♪Green on the outside, yellow within♪

08:59.180 --> 09:02.500
♪The sorrow in my heart♪

09:02.740 --> 09:09.580
♪When will it ever end♪

09:38.860 --> 09:40.500
You've always been meticulous

09:40.540 --> 09:41.700
and steady in your actions.

09:42.660 --> 09:45.500
How could this brilliant scheme
to topple Qingque Sect

09:46.340 --> 09:47.660
have failed?

09:48.300 --> 09:49.140
Originally,

09:49.380 --> 09:51.100
everything was under my control.

09:51.340 --> 09:52.940
However, Cai Pingshu's niece

09:53.180 --> 09:55.220
obtained the antidote to the Body Shift.

09:55.940 --> 09:57.980
Thus, the plan failed.

09:59.980 --> 10:01.540
Cai Pingshu's niece?

10:02.420 --> 10:03.580
How is her martial skill?

10:03.780 --> 10:05.980
She bears much
of Cai Pingshu's former presence.

10:06.980 --> 10:09.780
I never expected Cai Pingshu
to leave behind such a remnant

10:10.180 --> 10:12.020
to continue wreaking havoc on our sect.

10:21.580 --> 10:23.100
Chief...

10:38.660 --> 10:41.140
(Sun Ruoshui, Li Sect)

10:42.820 --> 10:43.660
Chief.

10:43.820 --> 10:44.660
Do you know

10:44.980 --> 10:46.660
your son has returned?

10:48.580 --> 10:49.420
Impossible.

10:52.620 --> 10:53.940
He's back,

10:54.820 --> 10:57.620
unaffected by your poison.

10:57.780 --> 10:58.620
Impossible.

10:58.700 --> 10:59.940
Chief, you must believe me.

10:59.940 --> 11:01.020
This poison has no cure.

11:01.660 --> 11:02.500
Mu...

11:05.260 --> 11:06.100
He is

11:06.700 --> 11:07.740
just struggling to live.

11:07.940 --> 11:09.380
He'll die soon.

11:13.060 --> 11:14.460
Of course, I believe you.

11:15.820 --> 11:17.260
But isn't this too coincidental?

11:18.580 --> 11:20.180
He appeared

11:20.780 --> 11:22.420
precisely when the strategist

11:22.620 --> 11:23.820
screwed up the plan.

11:34.380 --> 11:36.060
Where did Chang Ning of Chang Fort go?

11:36.620 --> 11:38.180
Why is there not the slightest clue

11:38.307 --> 11:39.613
about the item we're looking for?

11:39.624 --> 11:41.220
After Chang Ning went down the mountain,

11:41.231 --> 11:42.333
he vanished without a trace.

11:42.620 --> 11:44.900
I've sent people to search everywhere.

11:45.100 --> 11:46.860
Make sure to find that item.

11:46.940 --> 11:48.060
Understood.

11:49.220 --> 11:51.340
Time to think about how to deal
with Mu Qingyan.

11:54.780 --> 11:55.740
Elder Hufa,

11:56.300 --> 11:57.140
what do you think?

12:04.940 --> 12:07.740
(Hu Fengge, Elder Hufa of Li Sect)

12:08.340 --> 12:09.460
Rest assured, Chief.

12:10.780 --> 12:11.620
Once he comes,

12:12.380 --> 12:13.220
he will surely die.

12:13.860 --> 12:15.060
With you and the strategist,

12:16.020 --> 12:17.580
I naturally feel at ease.

12:36.900 --> 12:38.100
Cai Pingshu's niece

12:38.500 --> 12:39.740
has such courage.

12:40.780 --> 12:42.140
I was careless and got struck

12:43.300 --> 12:45.060
by Qi Yunke's Huolong Palm.

12:47.227 --> 12:48.427
Had I known this would happen,

12:49.020 --> 12:50.180
I should've gone with you.

12:53.900 --> 12:55.420
If you didn't stay in Bliss Palace,

12:56.540 --> 12:57.380
how could I

12:58.660 --> 12:59.980
be at ease outside?

13:03.660 --> 13:05.140
Mu Qingyan has returned

13:05.820 --> 13:07.940
with better martial strength.

13:09.620 --> 13:10.460
Maybe

13:10.820 --> 13:12.460
he cultivated some miraculous method.

13:13.900 --> 13:14.740
Moreover,

13:15.180 --> 13:16.180
Qinong's token has fallen

13:16.900 --> 13:19.220
into Cai Pingshu's niece's hands.

13:19.780 --> 13:20.620
I fear

13:20.940 --> 13:22.540
Qinong and Elder Tianji

13:24.700 --> 13:25.900
are already dead.

13:26.860 --> 13:28.186
With troubles within and without,

13:28.540 --> 13:29.580
in these turbulent times,

13:30.620 --> 13:31.460
you and I

13:33.300 --> 13:35.060
must not be careless.

13:44.466 --> 13:46.615
(To Zhao, my daughter)
Yuzhi, my mother has replied.

13:46.740 --> 13:48.820
This treasure is called Jade Sunflower.

13:48.980 --> 13:51.020
It was stolen
from the demonic sect's treasury

13:51.020 --> 13:52.040
by my aunt's close friend.

13:52.140 --> 13:54.300
After curing
the Shi brothers' Nether Aura,

13:54.700 --> 13:55.973
its whereabouts became unknown.

13:56.340 --> 13:57.180
So,

13:58.060 --> 13:59.100
there is still no clue.

13:59.660 --> 14:00.500
I suspect

14:00.859 --> 14:02.620
it returned
to the demonic sect's treasury.

14:02.700 --> 14:03.540
How do you know?

14:04.060 --> 14:05.540
My aunt acted with integrity.

14:05.700 --> 14:06.553
She wouldn't keep

14:06.564 --> 14:08.020
a demonic sect treasure for herself.

14:08.620 --> 14:10.540
I think after using the Jade Sunflower,

14:11.100 --> 14:12.220
she returned it intact.

14:12.540 --> 14:14.060
Ms. Cai truly was such a person.

14:17.300 --> 14:19.260
Why don't we go steal it

14:19.460 --> 14:21.140
from the demonic sect treasury?

14:21.260 --> 14:22.980
The demonic sect is in great turmoil.

14:23.180 --> 14:24.020
It's not that simple.

14:24.340 --> 14:25.260
What are you two doing?

14:28.540 --> 14:29.500
What are you two doing?

14:30.380 --> 14:31.980
We're discussing important matters.

14:32.180 --> 14:34.373
What important matter
requires discussing face-to-face?

14:34.700 --> 14:35.900
- Lingbo, I...
- Quiet.

14:35.940 --> 14:36.780
I wasn't asking you.

14:38.660 --> 14:39.620
I can't tell you now.

14:39.700 --> 14:40.700
Even to me?

14:41.460 --> 14:42.540
But you can tell her?

14:43.340 --> 14:44.380
Lingbo, actually...

14:44.380 --> 14:45.413
No need to explain to her.

14:46.540 --> 14:47.380
Qi Lingbo,

14:47.940 --> 14:49.420
have you already forgotten

14:49.431 --> 14:50.660
what you said to me days ago?

14:54.860 --> 14:55.700
Yuzhi,

14:56.700 --> 14:58.340
do you think I'm too stupid

14:58.940 --> 15:00.980
and incompetent to help you?

15:01.700 --> 15:03.460
Is that why you discuss
everything with her?

15:03.700 --> 15:05.020
Or is it you...

15:05.020 --> 15:05.953
You're overthinking it.

15:06.500 --> 15:07.340
I'm not.

15:08.220 --> 15:10.060
I'm the one closest to you.

15:11.140 --> 15:12.500
Yet now, you're not even willing

15:12.500 --> 15:14.100
to talk to me.

15:16.300 --> 15:17.140
Well,

15:18.380 --> 15:19.460
sorry to interrupt you two.

15:20.553 --> 15:21.540
I'll take my leave first.

15:22.700 --> 15:24.020
Cai Zhao, stop right there.

15:24.020 --> 15:25.140
Cai Zhao, stop right there!

15:26.500 --> 15:27.340
Cai Zhao!

15:29.980 --> 15:30.820
Father.

15:30.860 --> 15:31.700
Uncle.

15:34.660 --> 15:35.500
You're bleeding.

15:45.500 --> 15:46.340
Son,

15:46.720 --> 15:47.755
didn't you use to dislike

15:47.766 --> 15:49.500
these gold and silver vulgarities
the most?

15:49.700 --> 15:51.980
Why have people deliver these this time?

15:52.500 --> 15:53.460
Zhao likes them.

15:53.739 --> 15:54.820
Compared to refined objects,

15:55.140 --> 15:56.580
she seems to prefer gold and silver.

15:58.900 --> 16:00.500
These are for Zhao?

16:04.300 --> 16:05.420
You like her.

16:07.500 --> 16:08.340
I'm giving her these

16:08.705 --> 16:10.426
to thank her for helping me
find medicine.

16:11.126 --> 16:12.380
I'm still bound by a betrothal.

16:13.060 --> 16:14.233
Father, please don't say that.

16:14.340 --> 16:15.700
Don't harm Zhao's reputation.

16:16.140 --> 16:17.020
Son,

16:17.060 --> 16:17.940
listen to me.

16:18.500 --> 16:20.740
A true confidant is hard to find.

16:21.740 --> 16:24.180
Fate is something you must seize.

16:24.980 --> 16:25.820
To be honest,

16:25.980 --> 16:27.300
your betrothal to Lingbo

16:27.340 --> 16:29.980
was decided on a whim
by your mother and Lady Yin.

16:29.991 --> 16:31.545
I've always felt it was inappropriate.

16:31.660 --> 16:32.500
Coincidentally,

16:32.580 --> 16:34.660
Lady Yin invited me to discuss matters.

16:35.180 --> 16:36.820
I can just help you annul the betrothal.

16:37.100 --> 16:37.940
Father,

16:38.140 --> 16:39.180
a betrothal is serious.

16:40.260 --> 16:42.780
Even if I have no feelings for Lingbo,

16:42.793 --> 16:44.173
I must first report this to Master.

16:45.020 --> 16:45.860
Moreover,

16:46.086 --> 16:47.720
the sect's turmoil
has only just settled,

16:48.300 --> 16:49.740
and Senior Qiu just died.

16:50.486 --> 16:51.860
If we break off the betrothal now,

16:51.940 --> 16:53.813
everyone will think Lingbo despises me

16:53.824 --> 16:55.010
for being injured and useless.

16:55.620 --> 16:57.540
How would Lingbo
face herself in the future?

16:58.900 --> 16:59.740
Son,

16:59.860 --> 17:01.940
you always hesitate like this.

17:02.620 --> 17:04.140
What if Zhao leaves you?

17:05.300 --> 17:06.460
I still need to cultivate.

17:07.260 --> 17:08.100
Goodbye.

17:08.300 --> 17:09.140
You...

17:18.260 --> 17:19.860
Look, the fish have grown quite a bit.

17:19.980 --> 17:20.820
Feed them some more.

17:22.500 --> 17:23.340
Look at that one.

17:24.140 --> 17:26.980
I heard Yuzhi sent
a lot of valuables to Zhao.

17:27.100 --> 17:28.300
Shijun, do you know about it?

17:29.500 --> 17:31.020
The saliva Zhao sent over

17:31.020 --> 17:32.580
is truly good stuff.

17:32.660 --> 17:33.900
Yuzhi used it in his medicine,

17:33.980 --> 17:35.940
and the cold energy
in his body decreased a lot.

17:35.980 --> 17:36.860
With such great merit,

17:37.220 --> 17:38.700
even sending more treasures

17:38.820 --> 17:39.900
would be only proper.

17:41.940 --> 17:44.300
Zhao did a great service this time.

17:46.500 --> 17:47.460
Back then,

17:47.620 --> 17:48.980
Pingshu's grace and bearing

17:49.100 --> 17:50.500
were already breathtaking.

17:51.220 --> 17:53.660
What a surprise that her niece
would be just as outstanding.

17:54.140 --> 17:55.140
So young,

17:55.293 --> 17:56.593
yet calm in the face of trouble,

17:56.820 --> 17:57.700
brave and resourceful,

17:57.900 --> 17:59.166
worthy of great responsibility.

17:59.380 --> 18:02.140
The Cais did a great job in parenting.

18:03.460 --> 18:05.900
Yuzhi also showed
the air of a great general.

18:06.100 --> 18:07.460
If not for his steady response,

18:07.820 --> 18:10.020
there might've been complications.

18:10.460 --> 18:11.980
Shijun, have some tea.

18:16.580 --> 18:19.260
Yuzhi naturally carries
my old style and spirit.

18:24.980 --> 18:26.780
I only hate the Nether Aura.

18:27.540 --> 18:28.580
Once I leave,

18:28.940 --> 18:30.380
even if I wear out iron shoes

18:30.499 --> 18:31.533
and spend all my wealth,

18:31.544 --> 18:33.433
I'll try my best to find
more medicine for him.

18:33.940 --> 18:34.980
Are you going to leave?

18:35.700 --> 18:36.540
Yes.

18:36.700 --> 18:38.420
There are many matters in the sect,

18:38.580 --> 18:40.140
all borne by Xiuzhi alone.

18:40.140 --> 18:41.540
I can't set my mind at ease.

18:42.260 --> 18:43.380
Since you're about to leave,

18:43.380 --> 18:44.660
why not take these two days

18:45.140 --> 18:47.900
to set Lingbo and Yuzhi's wedding date?

18:48.220 --> 18:50.860
It will also make it easier for Lingbo
to take care of Yuzhi.

18:52.500 --> 18:53.340
Well.

18:54.360 --> 18:55.260
There's no rush.

18:55.300 --> 18:56.140
No rush.

18:57.620 --> 18:59.180
Let's wait until Yuzhi recovers.

18:59.460 --> 19:01.180
What if his injury never heals?

19:03.580 --> 19:05.020
Yuzhi is still young.

19:05.340 --> 19:06.300
One year, two years,

19:06.500 --> 19:07.700
at most three or five years.

19:07.700 --> 19:08.940
He will recover eventually.

19:09.460 --> 19:10.300
As for the marriage,

19:10.740 --> 19:11.780
we can decide later.

19:45.140 --> 19:45.980
Let me see.

19:49.620 --> 19:50.620
Milady,

19:51.020 --> 19:52.260
you don't need to do

19:52.540 --> 19:54.820
such rough work.

19:55.380 --> 19:57.220
Just have the servants do it.

19:58.380 --> 19:59.460
No.

19:59.780 --> 20:01.620
This is something close to Yuzhi.

20:02.060 --> 20:03.460
How could I let others handle it?

20:04.200 --> 20:05.200
It's getting cold.

20:05.460 --> 20:07.020
I need to finish it quickly for Yuzhi.

20:07.180 --> 20:08.780
No need to care so much about him.

20:14.220 --> 20:15.940
Yuzhi is my fiancé.

20:16.260 --> 20:17.660
If I don't care, who will?

20:17.860 --> 20:19.860
But what if he doesn't have you
in his heart?

20:22.580 --> 20:24.460
Yuzhi and I grew up together.

20:24.563 --> 20:26.032
How could he not have me in his heart?

20:26.460 --> 20:28.060
It's just that he's been injured lately,

20:28.060 --> 20:29.100
and his mood is low.

20:29.660 --> 20:31.260
He is a bit more distant than before.

20:32.260 --> 20:33.340
But in the end,

20:33.500 --> 20:34.700
we do have a betrothal.

20:35.060 --> 20:36.820
The betrothal was decided by the elders.

20:36.967 --> 20:38.140
It's not impossible to cancel.

20:39.860 --> 20:40.700
Mother,

20:42.940 --> 20:45.140
the betrothal was decided
by you and Aunt.

20:45.506 --> 20:47.500
Before Aunt passed away,
she repeatedly instructed

20:47.540 --> 20:48.993
that this betrothal must be honored.

20:49.100 --> 20:50.406
How could we go back on our word?

20:50.740 --> 20:52.300
I made a mistake.

20:52.740 --> 20:54.220
Your aunt passed away so suddenly.

20:54.300 --> 20:55.620
That's why it was decided hastily.

20:56.260 --> 20:58.100
You know Yuzhi better than anyone.

20:58.300 --> 20:59.940
He only loves martial cultivation.

21:00.046 --> 21:01.020
His temperament is cold.

21:01.380 --> 21:02.620
He's not close to you.

21:03.620 --> 21:04.460
So,

21:04.780 --> 21:06.326
you told me to restrain my temperament

21:06.380 --> 21:07.740
and get closer to Yuzhi.

21:08.340 --> 21:09.460
After Yuzhi was injured,

21:09.471 --> 21:10.802
I showed care and consideration,

21:10.813 --> 21:11.733
attentive in every way.

21:12.020 --> 21:13.380
I've done all of that.

21:14.500 --> 21:15.820
But however you please him,

21:16.380 --> 21:18.180
has he ever been even gentler
toward you?

21:20.420 --> 21:22.460
I can't bear to see you suffer anymore.

21:22.860 --> 21:23.700
From now on,

21:23.940 --> 21:25.140
keep some distance from him.

21:27.700 --> 21:28.540
I'm fine.

21:29.180 --> 21:30.340
I don't think I'm suffering.

21:31.460 --> 21:32.300
Very soon,

21:32.460 --> 21:33.820
Yuzhi's injury will heal,

21:34.300 --> 21:35.980
and everything will get better.

21:35.980 --> 21:37.220
Stop deceiving yourself.

21:37.700 --> 21:39.700
The poison he suffered is Nether Aura.

21:39.980 --> 21:41.660
The chance of recovery is slim.

21:41.980 --> 21:43.820
He may never be the Lord.

21:44.300 --> 21:45.740
And you are the Lord's daughter.

21:45.900 --> 21:47.820
If your husband
can't love you or protect you,

21:48.020 --> 21:50.260
how will you secure
your position in the sect?

21:50.860 --> 21:51.980
What do you mean?

21:52.660 --> 21:53.700
Do you want me to abandon

21:53.711 --> 21:55.311
my fiancé because of his incompetence

21:55.322 --> 21:56.740
and marry another man just like you?

21:56.740 --> 21:57.580
Nonsense.

21:57.740 --> 21:59.700
Everything I do is for your own good.

21:59.966 --> 22:02.180
The Yins have operated
within the sect for generations.

22:02.180 --> 22:03.880
Are we to watch helplessly
as someone else

22:03.900 --> 22:05.260
takes charge of the sect?

22:05.260 --> 22:06.140
So what?

22:06.540 --> 22:07.660
What do you take me for?

22:08.140 --> 22:09.700
A puppet to maintain the Yins' power?

22:09.700 --> 22:11.980
Enough. How dare you accuse me?

22:19.740 --> 22:21.260
When I was lazy in cultivation before,

22:22.340 --> 22:24.340
you failed to urge me to improve

22:24.860 --> 22:27.020
and even told me stories
of powerful women

22:27.300 --> 22:28.700
meeting tragic ends.

22:29.700 --> 22:30.660
But now,

22:31.100 --> 22:32.780
I truly envy Cai Zhao.

22:33.660 --> 22:35.060
When the sect faced a crisis,

22:35.140 --> 22:36.220
she was brave and fearless,

22:36.540 --> 22:37.860
able to turn the tide.

22:38.140 --> 22:40.420
She can do what she wants to do.

22:40.513 --> 22:42.569
She doesn't need others
to love her or protect her.

22:42.580 --> 22:44.220
She can protect herself.

22:45.900 --> 22:46.740
Milady,

22:47.500 --> 22:49.180
Lady Yin is only worried about you.

22:49.660 --> 22:51.060
Is she worried about me,

22:51.140 --> 22:53.020
or does she look down on me?

22:53.740 --> 22:55.460
You were just like Grandfather,

22:55.460 --> 22:58.020
believing women cannot be lords,

22:58.460 --> 23:00.180
insisting on finding
a powerful husband,

23:00.540 --> 23:02.420
until you met Cai Pingshu.

23:02.620 --> 23:03.653
Then you finally realized

23:03.860 --> 23:05.740
that women too can be powerful,

23:06.180 --> 23:08.060
brave, and unstoppable.

23:10.500 --> 23:12.900
So, you and Aunt harbored resentment,

23:13.420 --> 23:15.020
targeting the Cais at every turn,

23:15.100 --> 23:17.540
even using Cai Pingshu's tragic death
to warn me,

23:17.780 --> 23:19.189
wanting me to walk the same path

23:19.200 --> 23:20.740
of attaching myself to others as you.

23:20.740 --> 23:22.082
What's so great about Cai Pingshu?

23:22.093 --> 23:23.426
She died young.

23:23.580 --> 23:26.100
If I could die as spectacularly
as Cai Pingshu,

23:26.100 --> 23:27.420
an early death would be worth it.

23:32.180 --> 23:33.020
Lingbo.

23:34.020 --> 23:35.620
What did I say wrong?

23:36.340 --> 23:38.460
It was all Grandfather's selfishness

23:38.780 --> 23:40.900
that caused so many tragedies
and disasters.

23:41.180 --> 23:42.580
For the Yin's power,

23:42.660 --> 23:44.100
for the position of the Lord's wife,

23:44.220 --> 23:46.140
how many more people must you sacrifice?

23:48.300 --> 23:49.140
Lingbo...

23:51.260 --> 23:52.100
Milady.

23:52.980 --> 23:53.820
Lingbo?

23:54.460 --> 23:55.300
Milady.

23:57.260 --> 23:58.100
Lady Yin.

24:02.100 --> 24:03.420
Dalou, why are you here?

24:04.460 --> 24:07.140
I heard you were struck
by the Chaos Needle.

24:07.460 --> 24:09.940
Why aren't you resting?

24:10.420 --> 24:11.540
Thank you for your concern.

24:12.260 --> 24:13.460
I'm already much better.

24:14.500 --> 24:15.580
Master ordered me to come

24:16.300 --> 24:18.460
and return this to you.

24:31.420 --> 24:32.860
The Clearing Pill.-

25:26.460 --> 25:30.620
(Grave of Qiu Renjie)

25:47.060 --> 25:48.140
Since you're here,

25:48.980 --> 25:50.260
come pay your respects.

25:54.540 --> 25:56.820
Why did you have Dalou return the pill,

25:56.966 --> 25:58.106
yet you didn't come yourself?

26:00.220 --> 26:01.140
Since that day,

26:01.300 --> 26:03.180
you've been avoiding me.

26:03.700 --> 26:06.180
Are you bothered by my past with Qiu?

26:07.386 --> 26:09.100
When he pretended to be you,
we did not...

26:09.100 --> 26:10.980
I know you did not cross any boundaries.

26:11.340 --> 26:12.780
Then why is it?

26:13.300 --> 26:15.220
Qiu held deep resentment
toward my father.

26:15.540 --> 26:16.820
He left the sect long ago.

26:16.859 --> 26:18.180
One-sided words cannot be trusted.

26:18.180 --> 26:19.020
Dear,

26:19.780 --> 26:21.260
even if Qiu Renjie wronged everyone,

26:21.260 --> 26:22.740
he'd never wrong you.

26:23.900 --> 26:25.660
If he truly intended to humiliate you,

26:25.660 --> 26:26.900
he would not have repeatedly

26:26.900 --> 26:28.340
kept you outside his door.

26:29.740 --> 26:31.060
If he truly were a spy,

26:31.420 --> 26:32.260
even for appearances,

26:32.380 --> 26:34.100
he would've pretended
to be close to you.

26:35.060 --> 26:36.620
But he refused to approach you at all,

26:37.700 --> 26:39.060
just to protect your reputation.

26:39.060 --> 26:40.820
That was what let Yuzhi see the flaw.

26:42.740 --> 26:43.580
Not to mention

26:44.260 --> 26:45.420
that Clearing Pill.

26:47.220 --> 26:48.380
Are you blaming me

26:48.540 --> 26:50.180
for keeping the pill all these years?

26:50.900 --> 26:52.700
Then what about you,

26:52.700 --> 26:54.180
going to Luoying Valley every year,

26:54.180 --> 26:55.380
thinking of a bedridden woman?

27:12.380 --> 27:13.300
Forget it.

27:31.660 --> 27:36.180
(Grave of Qiu Renjie)

27:40.940 --> 27:46.420
(Qinglong Altar)

27:54.500 --> 27:57.340
(Lian Shisan, Li Sect)

28:10.420 --> 28:14.620
(You Guanyue, Master of Qinglong Altar)

28:16.460 --> 28:17.700
Today is Master You's birthday.

28:18.140 --> 28:19.740
There should surely be many guests,

28:20.020 --> 28:21.220
lively and bustling.

28:24.260 --> 28:26.380
Thank you all for coming...

28:27.980 --> 28:28.820
Where is everyone?

28:30.213 --> 28:31.500
Why isn't there a single person?

28:33.140 --> 28:34.133
This is bad, Master You.

28:34.813 --> 28:36.860
There are rumors
that you colluded with Mu Qingyan,

28:36.871 --> 28:38.542
just like your adoptive father,
Elder Qiu,

28:38.553 --> 28:39.329
intending to rebel.

28:39.340 --> 28:40.420
To avoid suspicion,

28:40.700 --> 28:41.740
no one dares to come.

28:41.860 --> 28:42.700
What?

28:44.060 --> 28:44.900
Me?

28:46.020 --> 28:47.140
Rebel?

28:47.980 --> 28:49.300
Isn't this slandering me?

28:49.300 --> 28:51.740
This is more unjust
than snow falling in midsummer.

28:55.980 --> 28:56.820
Shisan,

28:58.300 --> 28:59.180
bring paper and ink.

28:59.820 --> 29:00.660
Yes.

29:14.180 --> 29:16.620
This petition of grievance to the Chief

29:17.580 --> 29:18.780
must show some sincerity.

29:27.260 --> 29:28.100
Shisan,

29:28.853 --> 29:30.260
let me see your long, slender hand.

29:35.140 --> 29:35.980
What are you doing?

29:42.140 --> 29:43.460
Dear Chief,

29:43.780 --> 29:45.820
since joining the Li Sect,

29:46.100 --> 29:49.500
I've only known the Nie clan,
never the Mu clan.

29:52.740 --> 29:54.260
My loyalty to you

29:55.220 --> 29:58.380
is wholehearted and true.

30:03.180 --> 30:04.420
It's Master You's birthday.

30:04.860 --> 30:06.700
Why is it so desolate?

30:12.860 --> 30:14.340
Mr. Yu, you're here.

30:14.860 --> 30:16.780
My Qinglong Altar is truly honored.

30:17.100 --> 30:18.100
I heard that you stirred

30:18.100 --> 30:19.620
the Six Sects into discord

30:20.060 --> 30:22.420
and left them with a mess with ghostly

30:22.420 --> 30:23.460
and unfathomable methods.

30:23.780 --> 30:26.300
What a remarkable deed.

30:26.580 --> 30:28.100
What have I done to deserve

30:28.980 --> 30:31.260
your personal congratulations?

30:33.580 --> 30:34.420
I...

30:34.540 --> 30:36.060
I'm so moved that I could cry.

30:37.140 --> 30:37.980
Li Yi.

30:39.540 --> 30:41.380
The Chief heard it's your birthday

30:41.620 --> 30:43.300
and had someone find

30:43.620 --> 30:45.940
Elder Qiu's spear from the treasury

30:46.180 --> 30:47.460
as a gift.

30:51.260 --> 30:53.020
Master You, do not overthink it.

30:53.860 --> 30:55.180
The Chief means

30:55.740 --> 30:57.460
that Elder Qiu's position

30:57.780 --> 31:00.180
will sooner or later be yours.

31:00.180 --> 31:01.740
The Qinglong Altar guards the first line

31:01.740 --> 31:02.980
of our Li Sect.

31:03.260 --> 31:05.860
We will rely on you even more.

31:06.980 --> 31:08.980
Thanks to the Chief.

31:09.660 --> 31:10.580
Thanks, Mr. Yu.

31:10.980 --> 31:12.340
My subordinate, Li Yi,

31:12.660 --> 31:15.020
has long admired your talent.

31:15.500 --> 31:17.340
Today, I'll do a small favor

31:17.340 --> 31:18.780
and let him stay here

31:18.900 --> 31:21.100
to seek guidance from you.

31:21.540 --> 31:23.260
(Li Yi, Li Sect)
I long for your advice.

31:28.420 --> 31:29.660
Master You is unwilling.

31:29.980 --> 31:30.820
Then, let's go.

31:30.860 --> 31:31.980
With Li's help,

31:32.260 --> 31:34.260
we'll surely be like a tiger with wings.

31:34.580 --> 31:37.740
I won't fail the trust
of Mr. Yu and the Chief.

31:44.500 --> 31:45.420
Nonsense.

31:45.660 --> 31:46.540
Guidance?

31:46.980 --> 31:48.380
He's clearly here to spy on me.

31:50.060 --> 31:51.660
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)

31:53.100 --> 31:53.940
Father.

31:55.140 --> 31:56.100
Why are you here?

32:00.460 --> 32:01.380
Darn it.

32:02.660 --> 32:04.100
Who wants to harm me?

32:11.740 --> 32:15.700
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang,
Elder Tianquan)

32:19.700 --> 32:20.540
Father,

32:21.340 --> 32:22.420
you're magnanimous.

32:23.580 --> 32:24.620
Don't blame me.

32:30.520 --> 32:31.410
Who?

32:31.420 --> 32:32.260
Who dares to hit me?

32:34.980 --> 32:36.380
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)

32:43.980 --> 32:44.820
Father,

32:45.820 --> 32:46.820
don't harm me.

32:47.820 --> 32:48.700
You're magnanimous.

32:59.020 --> 32:59.900
(Spirit Tablet)

33:01.940 --> 33:02.820
Father,

33:03.580 --> 33:05.060
I know you died unjustly.

33:05.500 --> 33:07.300
But my life in the sect
isn't easy either.

33:07.500 --> 33:08.340
Every day,

33:08.900 --> 33:10.220
danger lurks everywhere.

33:10.333 --> 33:11.486
I'm like walking on thin ice.

33:11.660 --> 33:14.580
I'm already 31 this year,

33:15.380 --> 33:16.700
yet I still haven't married Xing.

33:16.780 --> 33:18.380
You don't even have a grandson.

33:19.020 --> 33:20.380
If you kill me,

33:20.980 --> 33:21.820
there will be no one

33:23.380 --> 33:24.780
left to worship you.

33:25.260 --> 33:26.940
Father, you're magnanimous.

33:26.980 --> 33:27.820
I'll kowtow to you.

33:37.980 --> 33:39.453
(Spirit Tablet of Qiu Baigang)
Rebel!

33:39.540 --> 33:40.380
I...

33:42.580 --> 33:43.420
Get lost!

33:44.540 --> 33:45.740
What a jerk!

33:46.220 --> 33:47.060
Go die!

33:48.580 --> 33:51.620
(Qinglong Altar)

34:37.241 --> 34:47.901
=Generation to Generation=

35:06.661 --> 35:11.071
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

35:11.636 --> 35:16.251
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

35:16.591 --> 35:21.156
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

35:21.681 --> 35:25.981
♪Free to wander in the world♪

35:28.926 --> 35:33.626
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

35:34.151 --> 35:38.441
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

35:39.101 --> 35:43.131
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

35:43.446 --> 35:48.571
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

35:49.146 --> 35:53.956
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

35:54.171 --> 35:58.341
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

35:59.066 --> 36:03.001
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:03.501 --> 36:08.776
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

36:31.506 --> 36:36.636
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

36:37.001 --> 36:41.371
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

36:41.636 --> 36:45.766
♪I freely roam in the world♪

36:45.951 --> 36:51.526
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
